Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Hello! Betmatch offers the original social solution for players and betting-related community by combining two (betting house and social betting) business models, aimed to build a durable solution for the emerging cryptocurrency-based betting market.  Unlike pure peer-to-peer and social betting platforms, Betmatch users will be able to place bets against other people or the Betmatch itself, and they will get a guaranteed payout in case of win. This will be possible due to existence of Betmatch liquidity pool, which allows the platform to back up any bet placed by the user, unlike peer-to-peer betting platforms, where players need not only to place a bet on the winning team, but also have others players place bets with the same amount of money on the opposite outcome.  Another major advantage of the Betmatch solution is the ability of players to place bets in generally accepted cryptocurrency, not in platform-specific tokens. All transactions will be secured and executed using smart contracts feature of the Ethereum blockchain.

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: As I know Betmatch offers its customers a unique betting platform powered by blockchain and secured by smart contracts. The customers use Ether to place bets on various markets without having to transfer the money, so they are in full control of their funds until they lose a bet. The external third party cannot influence funds, bet execution or payouts, these processes are automatic because of smart contracts feature. In this way, Betmatch offers solution to several issues: players can easily transfer funds in the form of cryptocurrency without delays and without worrying that bookmaker will somehow influence the payout. Thanks to decentralized nature of our betting solution, we offer full transparency and high security. We believe that trust and comfort of our customers are the most important things for the success of Betmatch platform. The services we provide and the beliefs we adhere to will bring an inner change into betting industry, which was long anticipated by players all over the world. I impressed Betmatch!!!

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: The Betmatch platform will actively generate revenue in four primary ways:  1. Betting commissions (for non-token holders and losers); 2. Betting wins against users (house wins against customer losses); 3. Withdrawal commissions from user wallets (from non-token holders); 4. Additional income (i.e. non-betting business-related income such as advertising).

Author: Tygrabandis2
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Who can describe me how betting works with smart contracts?

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Greetings, dear user! Storage of customers' funds is performed on contracts within the system. Customers' funds are under their personal control during the entire course of interaction with the system. The rules and "honesty" of the system are provided by the structure of smart contracts for storage of funds and the mechanics of markets (the contracts of the markets themselves). Within the system, the customers' funds can be withdrawn back only to their ETH wallet in case of a win or a return of the bet. In the event of a bet loss, the funds are transferred to other players who have won within the given market or liquidity pool. Thus, the most important part of the system, namely the storage and redistribution of customers' funds, is transparent and inaccessible to circumstances of fraud due to the implementation of a decentralized process.

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Although general public considers betting on sports to be a rather straightforward activity, where bettors just have to pick the correct outcome in order to win, in reality things are much more complicated. There are many pitfalls and nuances that should be considered by people, who treat betting as a way to receive income and want to profit from it. Betting has been a part of human life for a long time, and it is surrounded by myths, stereotypes and misconceptions, which make bettors, especially new to the game, get things the wrong way and lose money. These mistakes are the part of the learning process, which can turn a novice bettor into the professional one, as long as they are fully analyzed. But at the same time, the desire to minimize the number of mistakes is completely understandable. Being aware of the most common mistakes that rookies in sports betting do can help every bettor to avoid them. That is why we decided to point out these most common mistakes, avoiding which will definitely save you some money and good mood. Learn the details here: https://bit.ly/2FLtK1I

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: In recent years sports betting has become quite popular in Asia. Probably, it is connected with the technological advancements, since people got the opportunity to place bets online. Nowadays, the Asian sports betting market has become one of the largest in the world. When it comes to specific sports, Asians have an opportunity to bet on a wide range of sports including football, basketball, tennis, handball, volleyball, and some country-specific sports like Muay Thai in Thailand, for instance. However, football is the most popular sport for betting in Asia. Players can choose dozens of different leagues and it is not unusual to bet on some less known, low-division leagues from European countries. After football come volleyball and tennis. Placing bets online is  much more popular in Asia compared to land-based betting. In the last five years, football betting and sports betting, in general, has become a multi-billion industry in Asia and bookmakers can thank the Internet for this.

Body: Betmatch team uses every possible opportunity to not only improve its product, but also to attract the attention of new investors and clients as well as general public to its unique blockchain-based betting solution. We cannot stand aside when any major blockchain- or betting-related event takes place and prefer to be on the front line. Last week we gladly participated in the Blockchain Leadership Summit conference, which took place on November 23-24 in Basel, Switzerland.  During two action-packed days full of exclusive content and unique face-to-face meetings, more than 70 carefully selected, top of the mind entrepreneurs from all over the world presented their ideas to more than 2500 attendees, which included investors, politicians, executives and experts. The guests and other participants of the conference had the opportunity to meet Betmatch representatives Walter Komarek (CIO), Ivan Chebotaev (CEO) and Maksym Prasolov (Advisor) and personally receive any information about Betmatch project and its services at their exhibition stand and during their presentation. Body: On a global level, soccer is a kind of sport which people mostly bet on. However, it does not have the same meaning in the United States since Americans are more into American football. While baseball might be favorite pastime of the USA citizens, when it comes to betting, football is Americans’ passion. American Football however, is not played everywhere. Nevertheless, it is featured as one of the most popular sports to bet on. Basketball is the second biggest sport for wagering in the United States. The start of the basketball season gives bettors the opportunity to have seven full days to wager on games. And baseball being the most favorite pastime, has a third place in the top 3 sports for betting in the USA. After these most popular kinds of sport to bet on comes soccer, boxing, golf and hockey. Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: It is a common knowledge that the biggest catalyst for a multitude of changes in various human activities for the several decades was a breakthrough in technology, which presented world with computers, Internet and mobile technologies. The rise of these technologies greatly affected the development and popularity of betting industry, and the sports industry was not spared.  Traditional kinds of sports did not experience many changes with the massive distribution of Internet and mobile technologies, and even became more popular due to enhanced accessibility provided by them. The most significant change of the sports industry was the appearance and rapidly increasing popularity of cybersports or eSports.  Read our new article to find out main differences and similarities between eSports and traditional sports in general and in terms of betting, check out the list of advantages and disadvantages of eSports betting and share your opinions on the matter here: https://bit.ly/2P0RxdA

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: As any widely popular but controversial activity, sports betting is surrounded by myths and misconceptions. People in and out of the industry spread rumors, half-truths and straight lies about betting just because they sound right in their opinion and it can help saving face while explaining the reasons for unsuccessful  bets. It is much easier to blame somebody else for losing than accepting that your analysis was wrong or that the luck was not on your side today. These myths and misconceptions distort the true idea of sports betting, and it becomes difficult to delineate myths from actual truth and useful tips. Ability to distinguish fiction from facts can help any bettor to make reasonable  decisions about betting. We tried to gather some of the most common myths in the industry and to dispel them. Read our new article for more information here: https://bit.ly/2Tz4zCt

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Stox is an Ethereum based prediction market platform that uses decentralized oracles. Users can make their predictions to generate their portion of a stake for a specified event. Its token, STX, is used as a pledge to create a market.   Unlike its competitor, Betmatch is a blockchain solution for bookmakers that allows players to bet against each other and the platform itself. Additionally, Betmach gives its users the opportunity of providing their own sports analytics or predictions. Furthermore, social betting network allows the service provider to collect all or part of his subscribers’ bet volume and add them to his own statistics.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: There are so many options of sports to bet on. Some people even create betting pools for different kinds of sports. Undeniably, there are sports that are popular to bet on worldwide but still some tendencies vary from country to country. It won’t come as a surprise if we say that soccer is the most popular for betting in Europe and, of course, in the UK. But there has been a boom in betting since tennis jumped into a second place right after soccer. The same thing applies to United Kingdom, where soccer comes first and tennis has a second place as well.  And the third place comes to basketball which turned out to be not so popular among European bettors. Others sports for betting in Europe are handball, volleyball, squash and darts. For sure, we can’t apply this statistics to all Europeans since every person has different interests in sports and only he decides which sport to bet on.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Betmatch betting solution gives players the possibility to bet on a wide range of traditional, virtual and e-sporting events. Unlike many of its competitors, Betmatch uses Ethereum for placing bets and does not restrict players from betting by using platform-specific tokens. XBM tokens native to Betmatch platform are means of additional functionality and a foundation to a unique social system on the platform. In other words, players can use Betmatch betting solution without XBM tokens, but the benefits they possess make them worth purchasing for several reasons.  XBM token is a discount token, and it assures a discount on all system commissions on bets for token holders, including the opportunity to have completely commission-free bets within a certain limit. Betmatch also offers token holders an opportunity to lease tokens to players, who do not own them, but want to take advantage of their benefits. They will receive up to 50% of all system commissions saved by the players, who used their XBM tokens for betting purposes.  Interested in details, exact figures and simple explanations of the XBM token functionality? Check out our new article about the math behind the token economics and find out everything you wanted to know here: https://bit.ly/2Fr18uB

Author: Iasia98
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Heroes of the Storm revolves around online 5-versus-5 matches, operated through Blizzard's online gaming service. Players can choose from different game modes, which include playing against computer-controlled heroes or other players. Initially, no heroes are permanently available for use; however, players may choose from a list of heroes that are free to use from a weekly rotation. By using gold coins, the in-game currency, or through microtransactions, they can gain permanent access to a hero. As of July 2018, there are 80 heroes in the game, divided into four separate roles: Assassin, Warrior, Support, and Specialist. These heroes include one multiclass hero. In addition, there are currently 15 maps available to play, each of which has different objectives to secure, with some having different victory conditions.  Experience points, which can be gained by being nearby enemy units when they're killed, are shared across the entire team. When a team reaches a certain experience point threshold, every hero on that team levels up, acquiring slightly amplified powers. Every few levels, players may select a talent which offers a new ability, or augments an existing one. This leveling system emphasizes the importance of teamwork and planning, since a player's action can affect the whole team.  Players can also mount different animals, such as horses, lizards, or unicorns, to increase their movement speed, automatically dismounting when attacking, receiving damage or using any ability.

Body: The idea of using cryptocurrency for betting is not unique. After the appearance and continuous upgrading of the blockchain technology, it was vastly implemented in many projects including betting platforms, betting protocols and prediction markets among others. Unlike its competitors, Betmatch represents a combination of classical betting customer experience with advantages of blockchain-based services, blending several business models to hit a wider target audience.  Betmatch blockchain solution is composed of multiple modules, each of which contributes to the possibility of existence of a trustworthy betting service that attracts attention of customers and investors. The core technology that enables the project consists of several types of services, such as blockchain services, customer and social services and betting services.  Read our new article to find out details about every service and feature that makes Betmatch possible: https://bit.ly/2PntIlg

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: As Betmatch is completely transparent and dedicated to the community platform, the liquidity pool (the entire system’s non-user funds) is stored in a truly decentralized way. Unlike traditional betting houses, such operations as bet execution, payouts, deposits and storage of customer funds are performed via a decentralized network.  Betmatch platform also offers a unique social betting network, beneficial for both sports analysts and players that seek their advice. Each player can become a content provider and generate useful sports analytics, predictions and other relevant content, and regulate subscription rules for his services: from free subscription to a profit share from any successful bet of his subscribers. Due to politics of transparency, players will be able to see how good the experts really are at betting, and based on that subscribe to the most reliable ones.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: According to our market analysis, there are around 20 projects in the sports betting industry, which use blockchain as the base of their business model. Most of the projects use the following approaches: a betting protocol, a peer-to-peer betting platform and a social betting platform. Each mentioned approach is supposed to improve betting experience in theory, but in practice, many of them are not only unsustainable, they also bring new difficulties to the table. That is why the advantage is on the side of Betmatch project – a unique blockchain solution for bookmakers by RevelDevelopmnent. Betmatch team believes that combining several approaches and business models, choosing their strengths and getting rid of weaknesses, is the only way to truly change sports betting industry. Read our article to find out what makes Betmatch project a truly unique blockchain solution: https://bit.ly/2FfucFk

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Hello! Yes, we have one interesting article about the prop bet for you!  A proposition or also called prop bet is a bet placed on elements of a game🏉 that don’t directly affect its outcome. Prop bets have two purposes in the sports betting world. Firstly, they can be a great source of entertainment and fun especially for bettors who are new to a sport or don’t fully understand all the nuances of the games. Secondly, they can serve as a crucial piece of a long term profitable and winning🏅 sports betting strategy. For instance, earlier people placed bets on the color of sports drink that would be dumped over the winning coach’s head, or whether or not a streaker would run onto the field.  Prop bets allow you to use every piece of knowledge and every prediction you have about how a game will be played to your advantage. You have the flexibility to profit off💵 the predictions.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: We have explored the startups in prediction markets and traditional betting houses and have found only one trusted, decentralized, and operating project - Augur, which is currently operating on the main Ethereum network.  Other projects, like Bethereum, FansUnite, FunFair, are primarily focused on betting traditionally and are working on some similar business models. But they contain critical problems, such as liquidity (market making) and user acquisition.  None of those projects have the solutions to the mentioned issues, significant market share, or market influence at the moment. And in our opinion, to create a successful project means to combine trustless blockchain processes, ordinary non-blockchain services and a self-scaling social system that allows low-cost user acquisition.

Author: Feth322
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Which  problems does your platform solve?

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Our platform solves such player facing problems as:  * Slow depositing and withdrawing It usually takes much longer than necessary to deposit and withdraw funds. Using blockchain technology, we guarantee fast and easy transfers.  * Lack of transparency A player is truly at the mercy of the house when it comes time to collect payments. Collecting winnings, especially large ones, often becomes an issue of goodwill from the bookmaker. Smart contract system bypasses this issue altogether.  * Social betting problems Players like to study predictions statistics, provided by «experts» or more experienced players. But there's a lack of track record of such experts that they could trust. Based on our token economy, Betmatch creates an innovative social betting system that serves players, analysts and Betmatch itself.  * High commissions Holding XBM token grants user a possibility to bet without any house commissions.

Author: Feth322
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: What can you tell me about betting protocol

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: The Betting protocol is an infrastructure solution, and it might seem attractive at first glance. This model is focused on providing tech infrastructure to betting companies and business aimed to execute their own betting house or related business on blockchain basis. Local betting companies don’t need such a protocol. In fact, any successful betting company has enough funds to produce their solution that fits particular requirements. So, the betting protocol is just a good idea, in our opinion not related to the real business situation at bookmaker market at the moment.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: The tax on online sports betting will be increased in the UK. The UK's Chancellor of the Exchequer has announced a rise in British online betting tax to 21% in October 2019 to offset the loss expected from the cut in maximum stakes on fixed-odds betting terminals. The rise of tax on online sports betting was expected in the Budget, but some industry experts consider it may leave some operators questioning whether it is worth continuing to operate in Great Britain, given the current fiscal and regulatory environment. Richard Williams, Licensing, Gaming and Regulatory Partner at London law firm Joelson, said that although there had been speculation in the press that the Chancellor would increase the rate from 15%, the announcement that it will increase to 21% will come as a shock.

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Thanks for your support of our project. As you may know, Betmatch is based on the Ethereum blockchain, but Ethereum blockchain turned out to be insufficient for realizing the full potential of our blockchain solution for bookmakers, so our team started looking for other possibilities, such as using the technical solutions of our partners and even developing our own blockchain. So, be calm, our team do their utmost to minimize any influence of ETH.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Although the majority of professional sports bettors abides the principle “Slow and steady wins the race”, which is realized in using only bankroll money for placing bets, without tapping into other funds, and making reasonably small wagers, there are people in sports betting industry, who just want to get everything at once. Some of them are just die-hard fans that consider placing enormous sums of money the best way to cheer their favorite team or athlete. Others dream about the greatest one-time win ever and a regular life, full of pleasures and without worries somewhere on the tropical islands afterwards, and some simply have a lot of money and see no reason to play it safe. Read our new article to find out about the biggest bets ever placed for entertainment, for showing support, and in hope of the “big score”: https://bit.ly/2F8VdKF

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: The critical invention of Betmatch is an innovative social betting system, that serves players, analysts and Betmatch itself. For players, this model gives the opportunity to significantly reduce betting commissions in comparison with traditional betting houses as well as to use proven trust-based social betting service. For analysts, it is a unique opportunity to direct and trust less monetization of their skills, influence or subscription base. Moreover, Betmatch is issuing XBM, an ERC-20 compliant token.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Although sports betting has been around since the first sports competitions, and its history comprises centuries of development and transformations, it always received an ambiguous attitude.  Even when wagers were placed on the outcome of the Olympic Games in Ancient Greece, opinions were split whether activities of this kind should be forbidden or not. Even nowadays, while many people consider sports betting as a thrilling and sometimes even profitable pastime, others stand against it passionately. While some countries legitimate sports betting and receive a notable profit from legal betting industry into their budget, others consider illegal and treat it like a felony, which just further pushes the betting business into the shadows. Interested about attitude towards sports betting in different countries? Read our new article to find out: https://bit.ly/2PAItQZ

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Decentralization ensuring unprecedented degree of security. Follow this link to get more information: https://tge.betmatch.io/  To use Betmatch decentralized betting service, you'll need to deposit in crypto with just one click. After you have your balance, you can place a bet on the desired event and coefficient from a wide betting line. When the event is finished, smart contract automatically executes the bet. And if you win, you receive a trustless and fast payout  Betmatch has such benefits:  1. We're the world’s first decentralized betting platform that combines the classic business model, executed in trustless paradigm using blockchain technology and the social betting network as the second (community) layer.  2. The proposed technical and business solution provides customers with an original service of house trustless betting, using cryptocurrencies. Deposit, bet execution and withdrawal processes are executed with the help of blockchain network services (direct crypto payments, smart contracts) and cannot be affected by third parties.  3. The critical invention of Betmatch is an innovative social betting system, that serves players, analysts and Betmatch itself. For players, this model gives the opportunity to significantly reduce betting commissions in comparison with traditional betting houses as well as to use proven trust-based social betting service. For analysts, it is a unique opportunity to direct and trust less monetization of their skills, influence or subscription base.  4. Betmatch is focusing on creating not just a private business, but a community-driven system. The business model includes a significant (up to 50%) automated and trustless profit share as a reward of social activity (not of direct token staking!), that brings value in the ecosystem.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Points Spread  When you bet the spread, you’re betting on whether a certain margin of points will be met. There are a few different ways a bet like this can go, but here’s a basic scenario: If the spread is 3.5 points and a team wins by 4 or more, that team is said to have covered the spread. Betting on the favorite in spread betting is called laying the points, while betting on the underdog is called taking the points. Spread bets are most popular in football and basketball, where final scores tend to be higher.

The token allocation for the founders and the management team will be vested for a period of not less than 1 year.

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Nevada has set a new record of revenue from sports betting. The state posted a record-breaking total of 56.3 million dollars in September. Revenue rose for 27% from August thanks to the start of the new NFL season, accounting for 10% of total handle. The overall amount wagered also set records at 571 million dollars – beating October 2017’s amount of 565 million dollars.  Since the Professional and Amateur Sports Protection Act was repealed in May, sports betting has been legalized in many US states. In particular, New Jersey shared impressing numbers in recent months. However, Nevada’s September revenue should allay fears that sports bettors will no longer come to Las Vegas.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Betmatch, being a blockchain solution for bookmakers by RevelDevelopment, combines the classic business model, executed in trustless paradigm using blockchain technology and the social betting network as the second community layer.  As a rule, before betting people usually look for some tips, articles concerning betting, analytics and sports prediction. With Betmatch you will not have to make a research by visiting different sites or reading references. Since social betting network will be constructed by the users themselves, every customer will be able to choose one or many other users to whom he is subscribed. The subscription will provide the customer with the possibility of receiving a service that will include sports analytics, betting content and other features. And of course, customers will be able to bet on our platform!  Do not hesitate before joining us and you will be able not only to place wagers but also to get content concerning sports betting.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: If you consider placing bets on sports a way to entertain yourself or support your favorite team, you do not need any preparation before making a wager. Just choose the event you are interested in and place a bet on a sum of money you do not mind to lose. However, if you are interested in making money by sports betting and consider financial value more important than entertainment value, you should learn everything you can about betting, if you want to win. Sports betting is a hard work, only people, who do research, develop analytical skills, and design their own strategies, have the chance of becoming professional sports bettors. And what better way of learning about new things you know rather  than reading a book? Today we want to present you the top 5 books about sports betting, check our Medium channel for the full article: https://bit.ly/2yHfPnm. Read, learn and win!

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Starting from January 1, 2019, a betting rate of 2% will be applied in Ireland. It was announced on Tuesday by the Minister of Finance of Ireland, Pascal Donohue. It is expected that bookmakers will not be able to burden players with higher taxes.  The minister explained that the government’s priority is to level the playing field by increasing the tax for remote bookmakers and exchanges. Sheron Byrne, Chairman of the Association of Irish Bookmakers (IBA), explained that in connection with the adoption of the law, about 300 companies will be forced to close. In addition, about 1,500 people will lose jobs.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: We have explored the startups in prediction markets and traditional betting houses and have found only one trusted, decentralized, and operating project - Augur, which is currently operating on the main Ethereum network.  Other projects, like Bethereum, FansUnite, FunFair, are primarily focused on betting traditionally and are working on some similar business models. But they contain critical problems, such as liquidity (market making) and user acquisition.  None of those projects have the solutions to the mentioned issues, significant market share, or market influence at the moment. And in our opinion, to create a successful project means to combine trustless blockchain processes, ordinary non-blockchain services and a self-scaling social system that allows low-cost user acquisition.

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Sports betting has been a popular pastime for millions of people around the world for quite some time. The primitive form of this activity appeared many centuries ago, and during this time, it has offered fertile ground for countless stereotypes, myths and misconceptions that blossom in minds of average people. However, as all we know, a stereotype is an established pattern of thinking, a prejudice, often having little in common with reality.  In our new article, we dispel some popular misconceptions concerning sports betting such as the impossibility to turn betting into a source of income, its pure dependence on luck and certain problems with bookmakers. We also talk about the changed image of sports betting and shifts in demographics of sports bettors.  Check it out, find out some useful information and allay the fears around sports betting here: https://bit.ly/2qcaeko

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: You can lend tokens! And here's an example of how lending tokens to other users works:  A token holder has tokens which grant him a commission-free betting limit of up to $100,000 per month, but he does not use this limit. He is free to lend his betting limit to other players who may be interested in saving on the house commission fees of 5%. So he can charge other users less than 5% to use his betting limit. If he charges 1%, then the token holder would earn $1,000 from other customers who used his limit. Even though the token holder has not personally made a single bet, he has attracted other customers to bet on the platform using his tokens and has earned money for doing so.

Body: While sports betting adds to the excitement on the field or on the track, the jargon can make it feel inaccessible to someone who’s never placed a wager. And here are the basic terms each better must know:  Favorites and Underdogs The favorite or chalk is the team or competitor favored to win a contest. Contrary, the underdog, or just the dog, is the team or competitor deemed less likely to come out on top, with a longshot not having much else but a prayer. Someone who always bets on the favorite is a chalk player. Putting your money on the favorite is called laying the price, while wagering on the underdog is known as taking the price.  Hope this information was useful for you! Stay tuned to get to know more!

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: Here's an example of how lending tokens to other users works:  A token holder has tokens which grant him a commission-free betting limit of up to $100,000 per month, but he does not use this limit. He is free to lend his betting limit to other players who may be interested in saving on the house commission fees of 5%. So he can charge other users less than 5% to use his betting limit. If he charges 1%, then the token holder would earn $1,000 from other customers who used his limit. Even though the token holder has not personally made a single bet, he has attracted other customers to bet on the platform using his tokens and has earned money for doing so.

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: We have explored the startups in prediction markets and traditional betting houses and have found only one trusted, decentralized, and operating project - Augur, which is currently operating on the main Ethereum network.  Other projects, like Bethereum, FansUnite, FunFair, are primarily focused on betting traditionally and are working on some similar business models. But they contain critical problems, such as liquidity (market making) and user acquisition.  None of those projects have the solutions to the mentioned issues, significant market share, or market influence at the moment. And in our opinion, to create a successful project means to combine trustless blockchain processes, ordinary non-blockchain services and a self-scaling social system that allows low-cost user acquisition.

They use trustless public blockchains such as Ethereum and Bitcoin to allow transparency and remove the central regulation body. Sports experts can not only place bets by themselves, but create a faithful community around themselves and gain additional financial profit by means of generating and selling the relevant sports analytics and other unique content. Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service

Betmatch uses cryptocurrency called Ethereum for bets execution, money depositing and withdrawal and takes advantage of smart contracts feature provided by the Ethereum blockchain. Users send ETH to contract and receive balance inside Betmatch betting service.  2. Bet on the desired event.  After users receive ETH to their Betmatch account balance, they can place a bet to the contract on the desired event and choose coefficient from a wide betting line.  3. Receive a trustworthy and fast payout if you win.  When sports event is finished and the results are available, smart contracts execute a bet automatically, and the won ETH are ready for withdrawal. Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: ABOUT BETMATCH  Betmatch is a blockchain solution for bookmakers by RevelDevelopment. It combines the classical business model of traditional betting cases (but executed in a trustless paradigm using blockchain technology) with a social betting network as a second, community layer. These two business models perfectly complement each other, providing additional customer value and enhancing the overall net effect of the system.  Betmatch’s proposed technical and business solution provides customers with an original service of trustless betting using cryptocurrencies. Deposits, bet execution, and withdrawal processes are executed using blockchain network services (direct crypto payments and smart contracts) and cannot be interfered by any third party’s actions. Besides an industry-grade, classical betting service built on top of a blockchain network, Betmatch offers an original social solution for players and the betting-related community. This concept allows each customer or project supporter to construct a personal business with positive cash-flows or receive a share of the platform’s profit as a reward for social activity and community interaction inside the system.  ABOUT TOKEN   - Betmatch is issuing XBM, an ERC20-compliant token.    - Personal token holding allows the user to bet without any commissions. It means that if the player bets and wins in the end, he gets not only the winning amount according to coefficient with which he placed a bet, but also all commissions from his bet.    - XBM tokens can be “lent” to other customers. Token holders may want to lend their tokens in exchange for monetary compensation.    - On the future stages of the product development, token functionality would be extended by the opportunity to bet on these tokens (without house commissions) and stake them to provide valuable information for the system.  INTRODUCTION TO BETMATCH               HOW IT WORKS?  - Deposit in cryptocurrency with one click;  User sends ETH to contract and receives balance inside betting service  - Bet on desired event;  Placing a bet to the contract on desired event and coefficient from wide betting line  - Receive a trustworthy and fast payout if you win;  When event is finished, smart-contract automatically executes a bet. Won ETH is ready to instant payout.  ADVANTAGES OVER COMPETITORS  - Prediction Markets  Traditional customer experience, convenient for the majority of players.  - Betting Protocols and P2P Betting          Liquidity (p2p and protocols are illiquid now) A wide variety of events and bets. We aim to build a real-working and long-term business.  - Traditional Betting Operators  Easy and fast funds transfers. Trustworthy paradigm. No worries about payouts. Low (and even zero) commissions.  TECHNOLOGY   - Blockchain and smart contracts system  Trustworthy funds transfer, storage and bets execution.  - Professional bookmaker analytics  Dynamic coefficients establishing and risk management provided by our business partner.   - Other  Industry standard UI/UX. Delegate social system. Staking (discount) token economy.  FIND US HERE:      [/list][/list][/list]

Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: For many generations betting accompanied humanity as a form of entertainment. Historians have all reasons to believe that people have been betting on the outcome of sports events ever since the organized sports events started to take  place. Betting has come a long way since its humble beginning, and eventually it has turned into a hugely popular industry, a favorite pastime for lots of people around the globe.  Betting industry is gaining popularity because it becomes legal in more countries and more accessible due to advance of modern technologies. Shifting to online medium allows drawing attention of bigger audience and attracting the female players. Usage of innovative technologies such as cryptocurrencies and blockchain allows creating a completely new approach to betting and spreading of e-sports offers new prospects that can spice up betting industry.  Read more information in our new article: https://bit.ly/2CHtFK1

Author: Betmatch
Title: [ANN] [TGE] Betmatch - An Innovative Decentralized Betting Service
Body: According to the official data, the total income from interest rates in Italy increased by almost 20% compared with September 2017.  According to the published data, online sports betting provided a cumulative income of 139.6 million euros during the last month.  The results achieved by licensees increased by 19% compared with last year. Annual revenue increased by about 38% to 1.1 billion euros, almost half of which was achieved by sports betting, which amounted to 472 million euros, or 39.1%.  Revenues from online betting rose by 25.7% to 60.5 million euros, and the market was headed by Planetwin365, which brought 16.2% in September. In second place was Bet365 - 15.5%, third place Snaitech - 10.5%.
